{"tid":1744794,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金世正將SOLO出道","createTime":"2019-11-22T02:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T06:57:19.000Z","uid":74065,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"9c80947192e53aee3d22467cf4fad2842b716be6","tid":1744794,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1ChSDbG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1ChSDbG.jpg&h=a507d3f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《GOD世正》將SOLO出道。<br />\n<br />\n據多位歌謠界相關人士透露，金世正將於12月發行個人單曲專輯。 現在選定了主打歌，正式進入準備階段。<br />\n<br />\n金世正2016年在Mnet《PRODUCE 101》中獲得了最後第二名，以I.O.I出道。 播出當時以大大咧咧的性格和照顧他人的精神，可愛的外貌、完美的唱功和表演能力獲得了&quot;GOD世正&quot;的稱號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI.O.I活動結束後，作為gugudan的主唱展現了另一種魅力。 他在MBC《蒙面歌王》中展現了登上歌王戰的紮實的演唱實力，在KBS2《學校2017》中首次擔任主演，憑藉穩定的演技獲得了好評。 另外，在9月結束放映的KBS2《讓我聆聽你的歌》中，他以精湛的演技俘獲了粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n像這樣，金世正不僅是歌手本業、還是綜藝、演技、CF等領域都活躍。這樣的她透過SOLO專輯將展現自己的真實面貌，在12月出道備受期待和關注。<br />\n<br />\n88蛋收皮未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3d4de64d8578d09088763b03865fc6e4f204f4","tid":1744794,"uid":5008,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:13:03.000Z","msg":"睇左金正恩"},{"pid":"3557ecd39f765e362c792126f960bd43d1d54176","tid":1744794,"uid":34489,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"雖然好醜 但幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054d0f8b11786cf0dac216cab0cdf3f8bff045e1","tid":1744794,"uid":190258,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:26:11.000Z","msg":"遲咗兩年😭"},{"pid":"ccd3f1103a954245300f513c7e702c6c3cd18ae7","tid":1744794,"uid":184233,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"說好的2019IOI呢?"},{"pid":"a58cd11cfd4d3463527bf2e29a539a3d1dc2d0ca","tid":1744794,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3d4de64d8578d09088763b03865fc6e4f204f4","ti